            My name is Jeffrey Joseph Sy. I am a Toronto based software engineer who believes in personal growth and endless learning. When not in front of my computer I like to stay active by biking, hiking with my dog, and swimming. I am also a huge basketball fan, especially of the Toronto Raptors.
