            <p>If you would like to know more about me, please view one of the links below</p>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="../content/JeffreySy_resume_2021.pdf">Work resume</a></li>
              <li><a href="/projects">Ongoing and completed projects</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services">Services provided</a></li>
            </ul> 
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-3">        
          <img src="../assets/images/profile2.jpg" width="135%">        
